#

Truffle Mac and Cheese with a Crispy Parmesan Crust

$15.99
700 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianIndulgent

Tags:

PastaComfort FoodGourmet

Description

A rich and creamy mac and cheese elevated with the luxurious flavor of truffles, topped with a crunchy Parmesan crust.

Ingredients

  • Elbow Macaroni: 8 oz
  • Unsalted Butter: 4 tbsp
  • All-Purpose Flour: 1/4 cup
  • Milk: 3 cups
  • Heavy Cream: 1 cup
  • Shredded Cheddar Cheese: 2 cups
  • Shredded Gruyère Cheese: 1 cup
  • Truffle Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1 cup
  • Breadcrumbs: 1/2 cup
